The Basic HTML Tags

Tag			Description
<!DOCTYPE> 	Sets the document type
<html>		Starts the HTML document
<title>		Sets a title for the document
<body>		Starts the document's body
<h1> to <h6>	Creates HTML headings
<p>			Creates a paragraph
<hr>			Creates a thematic change in the content
<br>			Inserts a single line break
<!--...-->		Creates a comment


The 9 Essential HTML Tags

Tag			Description
<a> 			The important 'a' tag. Creates links
<title>		Sets a title for the document
<div>		Creates divisions in pages
<h1> to <h6>	Creates HTML headings
<p>			Creates a paragraph
<ul>, <ol>	Creates lists and menus
<li>	 		Creates list items in lists
<br>			Inserts a single line break
<img>		Inserts images into a page
